.B sungremlinfile
.RI ( SUN / X11 )
.IP \(bu
The second line of the file contains an orientation, and
.B x
and
.B y
values for a positioning point, separated by spaces.
The orientation, either
.B 0
or
.BR 1 ,
is ignored by the
.IR SUN / X11
version.
.B 0
means that
.I gremlin
will display things in horizontal format (drawing area wider than it is
