6 \(mi@@medium solid lines
.TE
.DE
.sp
For polygons, one more value, 0, is legal.
It specifies a polygon with an invisible border.
For text, the brush selects a font as follows:
.sp
.DS
.TS
center, tab(@);
ncw(0.1i)l.
